			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Vīrya</h1>
									<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
									<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
								<div id="contentSub"></div>
												<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
					Jump to:					<a href="#mw-head">navigation</a>, 					<a href="#p-search">search</a>
				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="hatnote">For the Hindu term, see <a href="/wiki/V%C4%ABrya_(Hinduism)" title="Vīrya (Hinduism)">Vīrya (Hinduism)</a>.</div>
<table class="infobox" style="width:22em">
<caption>Translations of</caption>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" class="fn org" style="text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:#FFD068">vīrya</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row">English:</th>
<td>diligence,<br />
energy,<br />
perseverance,<br />
enthusiasm,<br />
sustained effort</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row"><a href="/wiki/Pali" title="Pali">Pali</a>:</th>
<td><span lang="pi" xml:lang="pi">viriya</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row"><a href="/wiki/Sanskrit" title="Sanskrit">Sanskrit</a>:</th>
<td><span lang="sa" xml:lang="sa">vīrya</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row"><a href="/wiki/Chinese_language" title="Chinese language">Chinese</a>:</th>
<td><span lang="zh" xml:lang="zh">勤(T) / 勤(S),<br />
精進(T) / 精进(S)</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th scope="row"><a href="/wiki/Korean_language" title="Korean language">Korean</a>:</th>
<td><span lang="ko" xml:lang="ko"><a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EA%B7%BC_(%EB%B6%88%EA%B5%90)" class="extiw" title="ko:근 (불교)">근</a>, <a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%A0%95%EC%A7%84_(%EB%B6%88%EA%B5%90)" class="extiw" title="ko:정진 (불교)">정진</a></span><br />
(<a href="/wiki/Revised_Romanization_of_Korean" title="Revised Romanization of Korean">RR</a>: <span lang="ko-Latn" xml:lang="ko-Latn">geun, jeongjin</span>)</td>
</tr>
