<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="/wiki/Template:Parami" title="Template:Parami"><span title="View this template">v</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="/wiki/Template_talk:Parami" title="Template talk:Parami"><span title="Discuss this template">t</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Parami&amp;action=edit"><span title="Edit this template">e</span></a></li>
